  <id>org.qtforge.QtPlugin</id>
  <name>QtPlugin Library</name>
  <summary>Modern C++ Plugin System for Qt Applications</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      QtPlugin is a modern, type-safe plugin system for Qt applications with modular 
      component architecture, security features, and comprehensive plugin management capabilities.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Type-safe plugin interfaces with C++20 concepts</li>
      <li>Modular component architecture</li>
      <li>Security validation and permission management</li>
      <li>Hot-reload support for development</li>
      <li>Comprehensive plugin lifecycle management</li>
      <li>Thread-safe operations</li>
      <li>Cross-platform compatibility</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
